Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.80,0:01:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說人類上月球？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.90,0:01:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.43,0:01:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃得好飽 吃得好飽\N三頓都吃牛肉火鍋也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.60,0:02:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道是誰在付帳的\N還是「紅牛」的牛肉火鍋最棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.81,0:02:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外國已經在做這方面的研究了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.75,0:02:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要把人放進這麼大的大炮\N對準月亮發射哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.66,0:02:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過\N這個需要很多複雜的計算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.43,0:02:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我倒是希望你能做做\N吃霞氣讓肚子飽的研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或是可結出黃金的樹種子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.91,0:02:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你幹嘛聽他胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事連小孩子都不會相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.49,0:02:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說的絕不是憑空幻想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.42,0:02:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,科學發達的話\N人類一定會去月球的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.89,0:02:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我也想去月亮看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.43,0:03:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你\N你聽我說這件事沒有嘲笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎 要回去了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.01,0:03:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…\N能夠去月球真的很不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你笨笨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.42,0:03:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你講話很刻薄耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.02,0:03:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他的東西 他忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.36,0:03:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.09,0:03:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七十九話\N勝海舟與劍心\N活在幕末時代的二人的宿緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.78,0:03:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.48,0:03:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你忘記這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.52,0:04:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才離開沒多久\N東京就變得這麼危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.26,0:04:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 你保護這兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.25,0:04:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的東西 你振作點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的 請放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.66,0:04:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她比你還可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.77,0:04:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.92,0:04:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵馬！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.35,0:05:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管你是誰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想拿老師的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.66,0:05:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我大久保鐵馬\N就來當你的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.70,0:05:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情才剛要變有趣呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師 你沒受傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.31,0:05:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事 是這些人救我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.81,0:05:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你們拔刀相助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.15,0:05:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏\N正好當飯後運動是不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.15,0:05:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.75,0:05:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師 我不是跟您說過\N別輕易外出的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 是有這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師若是有個萬一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.27,0:05:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我送您到大屋去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.60,0:05:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎 你陪在旁邊\N居然沒盡到保護老師之責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.31,0:06:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 我已經受不了你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.28,0:06:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.29,0:06:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要在今後一肩挑起日本的人\N卻連劍術都學不好 丟臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.36,0:06:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 我不要這種徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 幹嘛說成這樣呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.76,0:06:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 那有這麼輕易就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.80,0:06:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們自己的問題\N請你們別插口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.47,0:06:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是你們認為這個\N滿口夢話的小子能讓人寄望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.74,0:06:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 這種事不試試怎知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.88,0:06:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為神谷活心流劍術師父\N我神谷薰一定可以把他教好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看是白費力氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎 在你劍術沒練好之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.83,0:06:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准再來登入我的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 鐵馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.94,0:07:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫做什麼 我問你名字呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.85,0:07:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫勝海舟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.44,0:07:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒完沒完啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.78,0:07:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別太沮喪了 你是男子漢\N應該讓他們刮目相看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用啦 沒用啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.38,0:07:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他要是有那個志氣\N就不會被逐出門牆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.72,0:07:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好過份哦\N不管那師父有多了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有這樣\N一句話就把徒弟趕走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.16,0:07:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們說的有待權商\N勝海舟不是那種冷血老人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.96,0:08:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝海舟不是幕末時代\N支撐幕府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.64,0:08:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護江戶\N面對逼近的薩長大軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.10,0:08:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做下「不流血開城」\N決定的男人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是通達荷蘭學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.28,0:08:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還跟遺美使節同行\N看穿時代潮流的聰明人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.48,0:08:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那位老人會在明治治世之時\N叫他學劍術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.82,0:08:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼想都很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管他以前是怎樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.69,0:08:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現況是大五郎無家可歸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這裏修行可以變得很強的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.86,0:08:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拚死練習一定有轉機的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那刻薄的老人！嚇一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.87,0:08:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對哦 我變強的話\N老師就會承認我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 就是這口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.15,0:08:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SCIENCE是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.98,0:08:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,科學啊\N西方專做研究的一門學問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本還沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.02,0:09:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師說那是\N今後的日本需要的知識…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有鐵馬那樣的徒弟的話\N老師才會有尊嚴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.63,0:09:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵馬是那位拿著怪劍\N的很神氣的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.80,0:09:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個叫西洋劍\N是西方劍術所用的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.74,0:09:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是鐵馬留學英國時學會的\N他的劍術很好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.68,0:09:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且年紀輕輕就前途無量\N當上政府的高級官僚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣是徒弟 我卻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.46,0:09:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你對科學比較瞭解吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算是吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.46,0:09:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你就就是有樣東西\N不輸給那傢伙了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.04,0:09:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 有科學的話\N就可以上去月球嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.64,0:09:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.24,0:09:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏 你看這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.31,0:09:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把人放進彈丸裏面\N再放進大炮對準月球發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.78,0:10:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是法國朱斯貝倫寫的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翻成日文的話\N應該叫做月世界之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.63,0:10:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.47,0:10:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼 大清早吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.57,0:10:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還問我幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.37,0:10:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎一直沒有回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.61,0:10:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過了 等他劍術練好再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.78,0:10:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎根本不適合學劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.78,0:10:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸你也這麼說過不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.78,0:10:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他喜歡做學問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好鑽研\N將來一定可以成為大人物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.99,0:10:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有說過那句話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.93,0:10:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 我去那個道場\N迎接大五郎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你阻止也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.93,0:10:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 你要是不聽我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你也不用回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.58,0:10:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 這個不明理的糊塗老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.08,0:11:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 你這麼急要去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.96,0:11:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過了\N我要去道場迎接大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.46,0:11:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 鐵馬\N你這麼早來有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.03,0:11:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來探望老師情況的\N我很在意昨天的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用擔心爸爸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.61,0:11:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.64,0:11:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…讓我送你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.98,0:11:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上班的途中\N曾經過那個道場附近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.79,0:11:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 就麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.64,0:12:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.14,0:12:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎今天起\N就是神谷活心流的門生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.11,0:12:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你等於是我的師弟了\N以後多多指教了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.06,0:12:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也請你多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.12,0:12:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼首先\N你去打掃道場的地板吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.70,0:12:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也得動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼我也得擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.53,0:12:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉嗦 這也是修行之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 他學得成嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.67,0:12:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有阿薰在教\N沒問題 沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.36,0:12:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.49,0:12:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 你很好的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.56,0:13:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸子是來迎接大五郎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說\N那個頑固老頭原諒他了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸說的話你別太在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.64,0:13:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說了 來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.01,0:13:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.68,0:13:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師叫我學劍術\N一定是為我好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個人有適合他的事\N也有不適合他的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不適合學劍術的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還有學問不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會替你向爸爸說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.53,0:13:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下\N大五郎是我的門生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.57,0:13:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能讓你隨便帶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.47,0:13:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大五郎是我們的書生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.78,0:13:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是被趕出來的\N被你們那不明理的老人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才來接人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.78,0:13:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們倆別吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你閉上嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.02,0:13:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係吧\N大五郎都說想留在這兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵馬！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.69,0:14:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐不必那麼在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣身為勝家的書生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為老師的眼光是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.10,0:14:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他沒有把老師的教誨\N發揚光大的能力與氣概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.78,0:14:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早點死心對大五郎也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.21,0:14:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且在這種道場實在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.95,0:14:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 失禮了\N我只是認為在這裏修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不會讓他功夫進步多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.12,0:14:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許這最適合大五郎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.93,0:14:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還讓這種小姐當師父…呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.23,0:14:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然你這麼講\N就讓你見識神谷活心流的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.30,0:14:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我學的也是劍術\N不過是西方的西洋劍哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.71,0:14:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵馬 不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.28,0:14:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心 我只是讓那位小姐\N見識世界的現實罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.75,0:15:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你讓開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.56,0:15:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.43,0:15:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是高手哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.06,0:15:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這種新時代\N還玩弄那種木棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你放肆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.88,0:15:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以打架呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 我得趕快上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.89,0:15:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 我要先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去時請小心一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.47,0:15:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我要暫時留在這裏修行\N請你轉告老師吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.58,0:16:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我懂了 既然你心意已決\N我也不再多說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.38,0:16:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我是不會離開這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.39,0:16:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說 你想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.66,0:16:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大五郎劍術進步以前\N我要留在這裏受你們照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.64,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？當然是準備晚餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.97,0:16:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.31,0:16:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.95,0:16:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留在這裏看大五郎修行\N至少讓我做點事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.92,0:16:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.69,0:16:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.72,0:16:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她做的比小姐的好吃太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.56,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是實話 沒辦法嘛 醜女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.53,0:16:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你累了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.10,0:17:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰是個很嚴格的人\N雖然看起來不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也常挨她的罵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.74,0:17:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 大五郎你真喜歡讀書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只有這個長處嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.93,0:17:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸子小姐果然還是\N適合鐵馬那樣的男人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.44,0:17:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.01,0:17:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道的 不管我多努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.88,0:17:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都無法像鐵馬那樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們同樣是老師的學生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.75,0:17:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是逸子不顧父親反對\N擔心你 來這裏了不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個 吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.58,0:18:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 這時候你要去哪裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.68,0:18:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去通知他逸子住這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去爸爸那裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.28,0:18:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用啦 反正又不擔心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.45,0:18:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來一碗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.32,0:18:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.66,0:18:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 擅自上門打擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏 沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.36,0:19:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在這麼大的屋子裏\N只有我一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.27,0:19:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸子跟大五郎都在神谷道場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.91,0:19:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 蒙你們照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那孩子個性很潑辣\N沒給你們添麻煩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.18,0:19:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的手藝好\N大家吃得非常高興呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多安靜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.74,0:19:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣獨處 不禁想起過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.44,0:19:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有沒有過這樣子呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.55,0:19:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候我想也想不到\N自己會有這樣的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因這過去我太出名了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.55,0:20:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要我的命的刺客相當的多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.16,0:20:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是開國 又是尊王攘夷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.23,0:20:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時\N大家都為自己的理想賭命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.86,0:20:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今回想那個時代真是熱烈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.10,0:20:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知什麼時候\N我看到了未來的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.44,0:20:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想身為活在那個時代的人\N我多少盡到一些責任了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.81,0:21:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的就交給年輕人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.85,0:21:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.92,0:21:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這話題很沉悶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.19,0:21:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就當做一個老人在囉嗦廢話\N把它忘掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.32,0:21:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝先生\N你是不是隱瞞了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.36,0:21:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.40,0:21:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸子和大五郎就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.10,0:21:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.84,0:21:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 現在該叫你緋村劍心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.72,0:21:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會照顧他們的 告辭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.67,0:21:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝先生是故意\N把大五郎與逸子調遠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.44,0:22:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一個人不知道\N想要應付什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.46,0:22:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們光明正大的走出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.00,0:22:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是昨天的那批人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.17,0:22:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准你再接近勝海舟了

